tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
  visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_url VARCHAR(255),
  user_id INT,
  entry_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  exit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  duration_seconds INT
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    session_id INT,
    page_visited VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
